#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.21"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.21:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.21:0.2"
msgid "3. Mahāvagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.21:0.3"
msgid "21. Sīhanādasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.33"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:1.1"
msgid "“Sīho, bhikkhave, migarājā sāyanhasamayaṃ āsayā nikkhamati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:1.2"
msgid "Āsayā nikkhamitvā vijambhati."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: catuddisaṃ → catuddisā (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an10.21:1.3"
msgid "Vijambhitvā samantā catuddisaṃ anuviloketi."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: catuddisaṃ → catuddisā (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an10.21:1.4"
msgid "Samantā catuddisaṃ anuviloketvā tikkhattuṃ sīhanādaṃ nadati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:1.5"
msgid "Tikkhattuṃ sīhanādaṃ naditvā gocarāya pakkamati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:1.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:1.7"
msgid "‘Māhaṃ khuddake pāṇe visamagate saṅghātaṃ āpādesin’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:2.1"
msgid ""
"‘Sīho’ti kho, bhikkhave, tathāgatassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ arahato "
"sammāsambuddhassa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:2.2"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tathāgato parisāya dhammaṃ deseti, idamassa hoti "
"sīhanādasmiṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:3.1"
msgid ""
"Dasayimāni, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa tathāgatabalāni, yehi balehi samannāgato "
"tathāgato āsabhaṃ ṭhānaṃ paṭijānāti, parisāsu sīhanādaṃ nadati, brahmacakkaṃ "
"pavatteti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:3.2"
msgid "Katamāni dasa?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:3.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, tathāgato ṭhānañca ṭhānato aṭṭhānañca aṭṭhānato yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:3.4"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato ṭhānañca ṭhānato aṭṭhānañca aṭṭhānato "
"yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, idampi, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa tathāgatabalaṃ hoti, "
"yaṃ balaṃ āgamma tathāgato āsabhaṃ ṭhānaṃ paṭijānāti, parisāsu sīhanādaṃ "
"nadati, brahmacakkaṃ pavatteti. (1)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato atītānāgatapaccuppannānaṃ "
"kammasamādānānaṃ ṭhānaso hetuso vipākaṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:4.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato atītānāgatapaccuppannānaṃ kammasamādānānaṃ "
"ṭhānaso hetuso vipākaṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, idampi, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa "
"tathāgatabalaṃ hoti, yaṃ balaṃ āgamma tathāgato āsabhaṃ ṭhānaṃ paṭijānāti, "
"parisāsu sīhanādaṃ nadati, brahmacakkaṃ pavatteti. (2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato sabbatthagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:5.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato sabbatthagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, "
"idampi, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa tathāgatabalaṃ hoti, yaṃ balaṃ āgamma "
"tathāgato āsabhaṃ ṭhānaṃ paṭijānāti, parisāsu sīhanādaṃ nadati, brahmacakkaṃ "
"pavatteti. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.34"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: anekadhātuṃ nānādhātuṃ lokaṃ → anekadhātu nānādhātu lokaṃ (bj, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an10.21:6.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato anekadhātuṃ nānādhātuṃ lokaṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:6.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato anekadhātuṃ nānādhātuṃ lokaṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti, idampi, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa tathāgatabalaṃ hoti … pe … "
"brahmacakkaṃ pavatteti. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:7.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato sattānaṃ nānādhimuttikataṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:7.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato sattānaṃ nānādhimuttikataṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, "
"idampi, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa tathāgatabalaṃ hoti … pe … brahmacakkaṃ "
"pavatteti. (5)"
msgstr ""

# BB has “the superior or inferior condition of the faculties …” following the comms. It’s not implausible, but it seems to me unnecessary, and a little programmatic. Surely spiritual faculties are not simply better or worse, but of different nature and character, and it is this that is seen. The term is indriya-paro-pariyatta “faculty-other-comprehended”. The last term = paricca, which is normally used in mind-reading contexts.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:8.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ "
"indriyaparopariyattaṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:8.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ "
"indriyaparopariyattaṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, idampi, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa "
"tathāgatabalaṃ hoti … pe … brahmacakkaṃ pavatteti. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:9.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato jhānavimokkhasamādhisamāpattīnaṃ "
"saṅkilesaṃ vodānaṃ vuṭṭhānaṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:9.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi … pe … pajānāti, idampi, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa tathāgatabalaṃ hoti … "
"pe … brahmacakkaṃ pavatteti. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.35"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:10.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, "
"seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo "
"pañcapi jātiyo dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi "
"jātiyo paññāsampi jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi "
"anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe anekepi vivaṭṭakappe anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe, ‘"
"amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī "
"evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ; tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo "
"evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, "
"so tato cuto idhūpapanno’ti, iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ "
"anussarati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:10.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, "
"seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo … pe … iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ "
"anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, idampi, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa "
"tathāgatabalaṃ hoti, yaṃ balaṃ āgamma tathāgato āsabhaṃ ṭhānaṃ paṭijānāti, "
"parisāsu sīhanādaṃ nadati, brahmacakkaṃ pavatteti. (8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.36"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:11.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena "
"atikkantamānusakena satte passati cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe "
"dubbaṇṇe, sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajānāti: ‘ime vata bhonto "
"sattā kāyaduccaritena samannāgatā vacīduccaritena samannāgatā "
"manoduccaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ upavādakā micchādiṭṭhikā "
"micchādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ "
"vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannā; ime vā pana bhonto sattā kāyasucaritena "
"samannāgatā vacīsucaritena samannāgatā manosucaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ "
"anupavādakā sammādiṭṭhikā sammādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannā’ti. Iti dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena "
"atikkantamānusakena satte passati cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe "
"dubbaṇṇe, sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:11.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena …"
" pe … yathākammūpage satte pajānāti, idampi, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa "
"tathāgatabalaṃ hoti, yaṃ balaṃ āgamma tathāgato āsabhaṃ ṭhānaṃ paṭijānāti, "
"parisāsu sīhanādaṃ nadati, brahmacakkaṃ pavatteti. (9)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:12.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ "
"paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.21:12.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ "
"paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja "
"viharati, idampi, bhikkhave, tathāgatassa tathāgatabalaṃ hoti, yaṃ balaṃ "
"āgamma tathāgato āsabhaṃ ṭhānaṃ paṭijānāti, parisāsu sīhanādaṃ nadati, "
"brahmacakkaṃ pavatteti. (10)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an10.21:13.1"
msgid ""
"Imāni kho, bhikkhave, dasa tathāgatassa tathāgatabalāni, yehi balehi "
"samannāgato tathāgato āsabhaṃ ṭhānaṃ paṭijānāti, parisāsu sīhanādaṃ nadati, "
"brahmacakkaṃ pavattetī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.21:13.2"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
